        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per 10 minutes</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You would take bludgeoning or sonic damage. You're able to use your internal invertebrate physics to minimize damage to yourself.</p><hr /><p>You gain resistance 10 against the triggering damage and don't gain the clumsy, @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Deafened], @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Sickened], or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Stunned] conditions due to the attack or any ability triggered by the attack.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If you have @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Ancestral Resistance] (bludgeoning or sonic), you gain resistance 20 against the attack instead.</p>"
